//- Admin - Represents the admin section.

<!DOCTYPE html>
html(lang=`${locale}`)
  head
    include modules/head.pug
    link(rel="stylesheet" href="node_modules/trumbowyg/dist/ui/trumbowyg.min.css")
  body
    include modules/header.pug

    div(class="jumbotron jumbotron-fluid")
      div(class="container text-center")
        h1(class="mbr-section-title mbr-bold mbr-fonts-style text-center") âš™ Administration panel
        hr
        div(class="card-group")
          div(class="card" style="width: 18rem;")
            div(class="card-body")
              h5(class="card-title") Database
              p(class="card-text") Manage the bot database on the RethinkDB administration panel. 
                em Requires a standard Linux authentication.
              a(href="https://rethinkdb.idroid.me" class="btn btn-primary") Access to the database
          div(class="card" style="width: 18rem;")
            div(class="card-body")
              h5(class="card-title") Servers
              p(class="card-text") Get the list of guilds the bot is on and make it leave them if needed.
              a(href="/admin/servers" class="btn btn-primary") Access to the guilds list
          div(class="card" style="width: 18rem;")
            div(class="card-body")
              h5(class="card-title") Articles
              p(class="card-text") Post, edit or delete articles shown on the dashboard home page.
              a(href="/admin/articles" class="btn btn-primary") Access to the articles
          div(class="card" style="width: 18rem;")
            div(class="card-body")
              h5(class="card-title") Maintenance
              p(class="card-text") Prune guilds, enable the maintenance mode and so some other cool stuff.
              a(href="/admin/maintenance" class="btn btn-primary") Access to the dark side
        
    include modules/footer.pug

    include modules/javascript.pug